Description:
No annotation on the envelope.

  • Booklet: "Le Rubens d'Auxerre" (exhibition of The Death of Adonis in Paris 1961)
  • Essay (reprint): 'Rubens and Stimmer' by Frits Lugt, in "The art Quarterly", Spring 1943
  • Essay (reprint): 'Zur Antwerpener Frühzeit von Peter Paul Rubens' by J. Müller Hofstede, in "Münchner Jahbuch der bildenden Kunst" n. 13, 1962
  • Brochure of the exhibition in Cologne 1977
  • Guide of the exhibition in Cologne 1977
  • Booklet of the exhibition 'Rubens als Bürger, Siegen 1967' (2 copies)
  • Catalogue of the exhibition 'Rubens als Bürger, Siegen 1967' (4 copies)
  • Catalogue of the exhibition 'Francis Bacon, Siegen 1967'
  • Essay (reprint): 'Ein neuentdeckter früher Rubens' by Hermann Konnerth, in "Zeitschrift für Kunstwissenschaft", n. 9, 1-2, 1955
  • Catalogue: "Rubens' Leopards", 1973
  • Photocopies of "Rubens and Ioves Eagle," in "Paragone", 1970
  • Essay (reprint): 'Rubens and the Book' by J. S. Held, in "Harvard Library Bulletin", vol. XXVII, n. 1, 1979
